A 14-year-old girl student has been rape attempted while coming back from the school on March 18.
&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


Shiva Sunar, 20, and Kamal BK, 24, of of Shankar Pokhari VDC-8 were apprehended by locals on charge of attempting to rape the girl while she was returning home from Tribhuwan Higher Secondary School. The locals had handed over to the Karkineta Police Post.
&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


She was rape attempted near the Jungle of Shankar Pokhari VDC. The accused had tried to flee the scene after seeing other students coming to the incident site.They were taken under control and handed over to the police by the locals after she informed about the incident to the family.
&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


Both accused are working in the construction of a house in Bistapani of Shankar Pokhari VDC.


&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
The accused were handed over to the District Police office by the Karkineta Police post on March 18 for further investigation. The incident is under investigation, according to Sub-inspector Shyam Krishna Adhikari.

