t;&gt;न्याय&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;SA&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;SA&quot;&gt;दिलाउन&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;SA&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;SA&quot;&gt;सम्बन्धित&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;SA&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;SA&quot;&gt;निकायको&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;SA&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;SA&quot;&gt;ध्यानाकर्षण&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;SA&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;SA&quot;&gt;गराएका&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;SA&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;SA&quot;&gt;थिए&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;SA&quot;&gt;।&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
		 दुर्गा थापा&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; Surkhet/November 8
		&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;An inter-caste couple has arrived at Surkhet seeking security. Nanda Bahadur Tiruwa, 21, of Taliham1 in Jumla and Tara Devi Rawat, 18, of ward no. 2 of same VDC had reached Surkhet nine days ago for fear of ostracism by family and society.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The couple said that they left the village after their inter-caste marriage was not possible in there. &quot;We came here as our family and society will not accept our marriage,&quot; Tiruwa said. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Tara Devi is pregnant. She is planning to give birth to the child despite her families' rejection of her relationship. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Meanwhile, father of Tara Devi who had arrived at Surkhet searching for her is learnt to have taken her to a medical shop in Birendranagar for abortion. However, the health staffs had refused to abort the child citing that Tara Devi was six months' pregnant. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Dalit activist Narayan BK said that such incidents were repeatedly taking place due to non-implementation of laws regarding untouchability. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
		 Durga Thapa

पाँचथर । कात्तिक २१ गते
		&lt;p&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;NE&quot;&gt;यासोक गाविस&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;-&lt;span lang=&quot;NE&quot;&gt;६ की १७ र १४ वर्षीया दुई किशोरीहरूलाई दुर्व्यवहार गरेको आरोपमा रानिगाउँ गाविस&lt;/span&gt;-&lt;span lang=&quot;NE&quot;&gt;८ का १८ वर्षीय जीवन सम्बाहाम्फे र सोही ठाउँका १८ वर्षीय मिलन सम्बाहाम्फेलाई ०६९ कात्तिक २० गते राति प्रहरीले गिरफ्तार गरेको छ ।&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;NE&quot;&gt;रानीगाउँबाट घर फर्किने क्रममा हातपात भएपछि किशोरीहरूले खबर गरेको आधारमा यासोक प्रहरी चौकीले आरोपितहरूलाई सोही दिन गिरफ्तार गरेको हो ।&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;NE&quot;&gt;घर फर्किरहेका बेला रानीगाउँ&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;-&lt;span lang=&quot;NE&quot;&gt;६ स्थित उतिस जंगलको बाटोमा को ५ प ७६६ नम्बरको मोटरसाईल चढेर आएका युवाहरूले बाटो छेकेर हातपात गरी बलात्कार प्रयास गरेको पीडितहरूले बताए ।&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;NE&quot;&gt;आरोपितहरूलाई ०६९ कात्तिक २१ गते जिल्ला प्रहरी कार्यालयमा झिकाई अनुसन्धान अगाडी बढाइएको इन्स्पेक्टर गोपालप्रसाद ढकालले बताए ।&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
		 सन्दिप राई&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; Panchthar/November 6
		 Police have arrested Jivan Sambahamfe, 18, and Milan Sambahamfe, 18, of Ranigaun8 on November 5 night on charge of trying to rape two teenagers of Yasok6.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Two girls – one 17-year-old and another 14-year-old – had reported Yasok police post that the duo tried to rape them while they were returning home from Ranigaun. According to the victims, the duo came in a motorbike and attempted to rape them at the road in Utis jungle. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Inspector Gopal Prasad Dhakal said that the accused have been brought to the District Police Office and the investigation into the incident was ongoing.&lt;/p&gt;
		 Sandip Rai

