		&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;An 8-year-old girl of Bastipur8 has been raped allegedly by a local 15-year-old boy on October 19.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The locals found out about the incident after the hearing to the girl’s cries after the rape and handed over the accused boy to Lahan Ward Police Office (WPO). &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The girl was admitted to the BPKIHS in Dharan for treatment as her situation was very critical. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;WPO, Lahan’s Inspector Dhakendra Khatiwada informed that a letter was written to BPKIHS, Dharan and medical test was conducted on the boy at Sagarmatha Zonal Hospital, Rajbiraj. He added that the police were investigating the case. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
