&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The beating left Dhaurali's tooth broken and injuries to her ear, Limbuwan State Council's district secretary, Kamal raj Nemwang said. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Accused Begha, however, denied his involvement in the beating. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The district police office said that investigation of the incident is underway. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
		 Sandip Rai

Dhanding/ June 3
		&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;A woman has been stoned to death by an unidentified gang in a northern VDC in district. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Krishna Kumar Shrestha aka Sukumaya, 30 of Salyadevi8, a remote village has been killed by attack of an unidentified gang at Darkha on June 2. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The body has wounds of attack by stone to its temple, locals said. The reason and gang involved in the murder has not been established yet. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Police has initiated investigation by studying the incident site today.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Final rites will be performed after post mortem of the body at district hospital, famiy of the deceased said.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
