		&lt;p&gt;Min Shahi, 28, of Sukatiya-1 has been arrested on May 30 on charge of raping a 23-year-old woman of ward no. 2 of same VDC. The District Police Office arrested him after the woman who runs a hotel at Raraghat filed a complaint against him accusing him of raping her at her hotel on May 26. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;According to the victim's husband, Shahi had already fled when he came back hearing her cry for help. He said that Shahi had come as he had gone to catch fish.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&quot;My wife is being treated at the district hospital and the police have initiated action three days after I filed the complaint,&quot; he said. &lt;/p&gt;
