&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;A woman from Dovane VDC had died due to excessive bleeding while giving birth to a baby in the district some time ago. Though the District Health Office (DHO) has created awareness in rural areas with the mobilization of women health workers for safe maternity, pregnant women giving birth to baby at home has not stopped due to geographical difficulties, said DHO chief Narendra Jha. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
