		&lt;p&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;Studies of Janjyoti Lower Secondary School at Tharmuse of Lekhparajul3 have been affected as students protesting alleged mistreatment by a teacher have padlocked the school six days ago. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
