&lt;p&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;Students are in confusion as the school has been closed while final examination is approaching. Students padlocked the school on February 3 alleging that Sher Bahadur Oli, a teacher at the school mistreated a fourteen year old girl student studying at grade six. The victim said that the accused teacher had been mistreating her by touching her private parts time and again. However, the alleged teacher has been denying the allegation. He said some parents have been using the girl to defame him. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
