&lt;p&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;School management committee said that the problem cannot be settled as the alleged teacher is not presenting when called for holding talks to settle the issue. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-GB&quot;&gt;When asked about the incident, the district education office showed ignorance over the matter. The office has no information about the matter, district education officer, Ram Prasad Adhikari said. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
