&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;District police office said that Laxmi who was sleeping alone was found dead in the morning. DSP Sushil Singh Rathaur said that the deceased's feet had been burnt. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
