&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;A total of 238 women have been rescued this year, Keshav Koirala, regional coordinator of Maiti Nepali in Nepalgunj said. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
