&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The girl's family said they were not able to take the girl to hospital again as they were just daily wage earners and that it was possible for them to go on looking for the accused. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
