		&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Basanti Thapa (Rawal), 25, of Waligaun9 has filed a case of polygamy against her husband Dipak Rawal, 28, at the district police office Achham on December 16. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Saying that Dipak married Dhana Khati, 22, of Daiji, Kanchanpur as second wife, she filed a case against him. Police arrested Dipak and Dhana on same day the complaint was filed. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
