Banke/December 17
		&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Police have arrested Bhairav Shrestha, 42, and his 15-year-old son of Kalika5 in Bardiya on December 15 on charge of raping a domestic help.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
