&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;According to the victim, Shretha's wife told her not to tell the incident to anyone when she informed her about the incident. She had told the locals after running away from the shop on November 25. Shrestha had agreed to pay Rs 150,000 to the victim at a meeting held at the village on December 1. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The victim's family had filed the case with the help from Women Service Center Bardiya. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Meanwhile, police have arrested Lal Bahadur Thing, 54, of Basamadi8 on charge of trying to rape a 32-year-old woman at a jungle in Makawanpur on December 16.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
