		 Pratap Bista

Kailali/December 9
		&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The district court Kailali has sent Prem Sapkota, 35, of Darakh7 to custody on charge of raping a 12-year-old girl of same place. The court gave order to remand him for seven days on December 9. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
