&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;According to Inspector Kabindra Limbu, the attack came a day after the victim filed a case of gang rape against Suman, Mahendra and Bibek Limbu. Police had arrested Bibek among the accused the same day that she filed her complaint. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
